Clown in a Cornfield is a 2025 slasher film directed by Eli Craig (Tucker & Dale vs Evil). The main protagonists are Quinn Maybrook, played by Katie Douglas, and her father, Dr Maybrook, played by Aaron Abrams. The Maybrooks have relocated following the death of Quinn’s mother.
